{"tid":1884090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"K Kwong：Made in HK 可替換口罩不會收取專利費，濾芯售價低至$2","createTime":"2020-02-17T11:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T09:47:02.000Z","uid":1886,"like":608,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"dba3429fa2a63ee1bafef86c8daa8a9e0cd54900","tid":1884090,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"〔香港人，自救啊！Made in HK可替換口罩！〕<br />\n<br />\n搜購口罩難如登天，<br />\n即使搵到一億個口罩，<br />\n也只足夠全香港用數天。<br />\n<br />\n不過，幸好香港人靈活變通，<br />\n與其問人買口罩，不如自己造口罩！<br />\n<br />\n森仔今日參觀了由 K Kwong 博士研發<br />\nMade in HK可替換口罩計劃的廠房<br />\n了解更多有關詳情<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目前研發進度非常良好</span></strong>，<br />\n詳情及實驗報告，<br />\n預計會短時間內正式公布<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\nMade in HK口罩，<br />\n顧名思義，就是本地製造本地生產！<br />\n由布口罩套，到濾芯，都是Made in Hong Kong。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Dr. Kwong亦不會收取專利費，<br />\n未計布口罩成本，濾芯售價可以低至$2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></strong><br />\n￼<br />\n香港要人人有罩戴，就必須自救！<br />\n多謝 Dr. Kwong 以及一眾義工嘅付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102922707728081/posts/189960149024336/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102922707728081%2Fposts%2F189960149024336%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=d3820440\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102922707728081/posts/189960149024336/</a>"},{"pid":"675e31e6be59c24fcae0e5a983555f6696690590","tid":1884090,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1ad4c93b0c4f7df98a8db48168a21500080cb1bd","tid":1884090,"uid":306340,"like":270,"dislike":0,"score":270,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"記得登記專利<br />\n費事比支那人搶走咗"},{"pid":"1ffa35f970d61f69d4b87158d3387fdba8c1f0c1","tid":1884090,"uid":1886,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score